  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as an Invader of Earth facing off against hordes of Ghosts in this wave-based First Person Shooter. Choose your upgrades, from an upgradeable Exoskeleton, Portable Nuke Launchers and Giant Robots minions to UFOs that fly around blasting through ghosts! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/3c71abe4c2c2c600a22b74cc0cbcf357.poster.avif?t=1738781914\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/3c71abe4c2c2c600a22b74cc0cbcf357.webm?t=1738781914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/3c71abe4c2c2c600a22b74cc0cbcf357.mp4?t=1738781914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PLAY WITH FRIENDS ONLINE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/756a4dd4b6f000f63ca4b6bb1ec24595.poster.avif?t=1738781914\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/756a4dd4b6f000f63ca4b6bb1ec24595.webm?t=1738781914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/756a4dd4b6f000f63ca4b6bb1ec24595.mp4?t=1738781914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SUMMON POWERFUL MINIONS TO FIGHT FOR YOU!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/64ac86a51620db07483dd82ca6b48fad.poster.avif?t=1738781914\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/64ac86a51620db07483dd82ca6b48fad.webm?t=1738781914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/64ac86a51620db07483dd82ca6b48fad.mp4?t=1738781914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PLAY WITH DIFFERENT CLASSES AND UPGRADES!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/9c8680a7a024c63f7b17b1dfd19ba2cb.poster.avif?t=1738781914\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/9c8680a7a024c63f7b17b1dfd19ba2cb.webm?t=1738781914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/9c8680a7a024c63f7b17b1dfd19ba2cb.mp4?t=1738781914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/b6409a69f70e1f39fc539522b7e31d93.poster.avif?t=1738781914\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/b6409a69f70e1f39fc539522b7e31d93.webm?t=1738781914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609730/extras/b6409a69f70e1f39fc539522b7e31d93.mp4?t=1738781914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HOW LONG CAN YOU SURVI